    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 The default behavior is Global, which specifies the removal of the performance counter instance when no counters are using the process category.  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  If the <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterCategory.CategoryType%2A> property is <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterCategoryType>, the <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounter.InstanceLifetime%2A> value for the performance counter must be Global.  
  
